referring to himself in the third person. You can hear him getting excited about
math on the <a href="http://mathforprimates.com">Math for Primates podcast</a>
(with co-host Nick Horton), you can read his first formulation of the punk
mathematics philosophy in <a
	href="https://www.facebook.com/pages/The-Light-Fingered-Five/172284746149029">
