	href="http://www.kickstarter.com/projects/1541803748/punk-mathematics">his
	alarmingly successful project pitch</a> at Kickstarter.com.  </p>

<p> His credentials include a master-of-the-arts degree in mathematical sciences
from <a href="http://www.mth.pdx.edu/">Portland State University</a>, and the
better part of a decade performing improv comedy with with the <a
	href="https://www.facebook.com/pages/The-Light-Fingered-Five/172284746149029">Light-Fingered
